      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "First I need to rework the parasitic capacitances so that the coupling caps get properly redistributed along the resistor networks, instead of being redirected to the substrate as they are now.  Redirecting to the substrate preserves the signal propagation delay characteristics but eliminates all the cross-talk.",
